Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:03.23,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's something very precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:08.52,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:15.29,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:16.83,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't really hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:21.74,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, I have feelings for—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.18,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:33.63,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what were you planning \Non telling her just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:34.48,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.32,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:39.02,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to tell her that I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.00,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:45.48,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you saying you weren't sure\N if your feelings were romantic or not
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.70,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,just a little while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.15,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, so I figured it out just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:50.73,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,A second ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:55.20,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thanks to my brother, \NI finally realized how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.20,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with Serinuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.45,sign_1375_20_Ni,# left,0000,0000,0000,,Ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.45,sign_1375_21_Iga,# left mid,0000,0000,0000,,Iga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.45,sign_1375_22_Nana,# right mid,0000,0000,0000,,Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.45,sign_1375_23_Shi,# right,0000,0000,0000,,Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.45,Watamote-internal/narrator,all,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straight to the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:59.04,sign_1385_19_blush,# sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Blush
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:02.95,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to tell her how I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.20,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as I possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:09.69,Default,Nanashina,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get real! We won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.42,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:13.20,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,No one gets a head start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.93,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,He means we all feel the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.99,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,I like her too, and so does everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:18.50,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:20.72,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should all tell \Nher how you feel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.72,sign_1896_34_Totally_logical,#sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Totally Logical
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:22.99,Watamote-internal/narrator,all,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straight to the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.30,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell us! We've already—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:26.06,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:30.98,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I know, I don't think any of us \Nhave actually told her how we feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:33.10,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:34.89,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's not right at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:35.65,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:36.51,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.07,sign_2318_43_Ni,# left,0000,0000,0000,,Ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.07,sign_2318_44_Iga,# mid left,0000,0000,0000,,Iga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.07,sign_2318_45_Shi,# mid right,0000,0000,0000,,Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.07,sign_2318_46_Nana,# right,0000,0000,0000,,Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.32,Default,#text,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:39.07,sign_2335_47_It_s_not_,#text,0000,0000,0000,,It's Not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.60,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're all free to do as you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.39,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm going to tell her how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:50.67,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,W-We were so preoccupied by \NMutsumi's older brother that we...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.64,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We pushed the person into action \Nthat should never be pushed into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:57.01,Watamote-internal/narrator,All,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop him somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:19.82,Watamote-Title,# title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3562,1)}Kiss Him, Not Me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:29.80,Watamote-Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HE4A9F4&}Ki{\c&HFFFAFE&}ss {\c&HEBB27D&}H{\c&HAAA0ED&}i{\c&HFFFAFE&}m, N{\c&HB0FFBC&}o{\c&H87EEF0&}t{\c&HFFFAFE&} M{\c&HF39BCF&}e
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.83,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.94,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:34.99,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:38.43,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,There's an event at the end of the month \Nand my draft is a bit behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:42.03,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please come over and be my \Nassistant for a while, starting today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:45.55,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the month?\N You mean Comic Village, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.91,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll help in whatever way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:51.47,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.53,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd better tell Mutsumi-senpai \NI'm not coming to club—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.04,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.05,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I have to talk to him anyway, \Nso I'll tell him while I'm at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.17,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:04.62,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't called "carrier pigeon" \Nin elementary school for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.43,sign_5812_68_Determined_,,0000,0000,0000,,Blunt
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.43,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to let him know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.67,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that right? Thanks, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.53,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Appreciate it, Coocoo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.34,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me weird names!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.40,sign_6071_73_Coo_coo,# sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Coo, coo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.74,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.56,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.52,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You too, Igarashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:25.65,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want? No one invited you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.03,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd leave the two of you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.30,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I thought I had my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.58,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.46,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:40.21,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Igarashi-senpai, can you \Nplease scan and clean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.49,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm going to borrow the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.78,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.38,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.84,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, situation update.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.72,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I've just arranged things with \NSerinuma's older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:58.24,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll stop Senpai from \Nmaking any contact with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.61,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm surprised you\Nwere able to persuade him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.19,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I told him Mutsumi-senpai \Nwas going a bit wild
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.61,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,and Serinuma might be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.95,Watamote-flashback,Takuro,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what a guy like him could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.95,sign_7375_94_A_bit_traumatize,# text,0000,0000,0000,,A Bit Traumatized
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:11.42,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,And there you have it. Mission complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.16,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.78,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Good. That's one thing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:14.83,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Nishina, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.83,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going well here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.75,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I've blocked Mutsumi-senpai's \Nnumber on her phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.88,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get cracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.50,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let Mutsumi-senpai \Ntell her anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.14,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how dirty we have to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.64,sign_22258_340_This_is_the_Hist,# sign,0000,0000,0000,,This is the History Club. \NWe're Always Looking For New Members!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.14,Watamote-internal/narrator,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,The number you are trying to \Nreach is currently unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.56,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Ono no Imoko was a guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.10,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.44,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-kun, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:45.81,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in Japanese history! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.45,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:51.34,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Soga no Umako was a guy, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.70,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.91,sign_8457_113_Serinuma_san,# phone,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.48,Watamote-internal/narrator,phone,0000,0000,0000,,The number you are trying to \Nreach is currently unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.25,sign_8557_115_A_few_days_later,# box,0000,0000,0000,,A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.25,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,So? How are things going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:02.91,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I've been having her over every\N day for the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.51,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,For now, she doesn't appear\N to suspect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.85,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.64,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, I got word from Takuro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.93,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, a telegram was delivered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.47,Watamote-flashback,Takuro,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.56,sign_8919_123_This_isn_t_good_,# right text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.56,sign_8919_124_Eep_,# left text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.56,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,A telegram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.20,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,And all it said was, "I like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.77,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we've gotten this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.06,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,It's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.69,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully he'll eventually give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.43,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:32.08,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you make it to Serinuma-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.32,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.09,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.29,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.04,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,He actually escaped out the window?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.63,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,He got me! And this is the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.09,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Shino?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.34,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, he got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.43,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I lost track of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.70,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:02.64,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma Kae-san from Class 2-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.01,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mutsumi Asuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.15,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:09.45,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please meet me on \Nthe roof today after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.19,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Mutsumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.92,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.01,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.78,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:18.63,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.30,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes this broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.19,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.82,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,How could you be so bold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.25,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you make a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.14,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.17,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,why are you trying so hard to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:37.21,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're all free to \Ntell her how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.15,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.64,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.07,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Those who want to tell her \Ncan come to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.58,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.53,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,And so, in this case,\N you use the formula to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.35,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,What Mutsumi-san said makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:01.50,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like she'll just return my \Nfeelings if I get in someone else's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.38,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell her, or nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.42,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarshi,0000,0000,0000,,But, if I do tell her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.67,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarshi,0000,0000,0000,,will she still smile the \Nsame way she does now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.53,sign_11715_168_squeeze,#sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,600)}Squeeze
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:18.14,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,If her heart does belong to one person,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.89,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,what happens if I'm not that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:26.26,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Still, the thing I'm hoping for most
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.02,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,is that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.31,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,...the only one for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.67,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.14,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.38,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:05.14,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like, why is everyone \Nhere? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:09.99,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to come so I could \Ntell you how I feel about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.11,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.09,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.07,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.70,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.71,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.01,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.04,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I like you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.70,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, I really do like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:40.34,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:52.78,Watamote-Eyecatch1,# eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,Ki{\c&HDB08B1&}s{\c&HD94A5F&}s {\c&HC6D878&}Hi{\c&HA0F962&}m, {\c&H55FFC2&}N{\c&H45CBE5&}o{\c&H4D5BD9&}t {\c&H451CCC&}M{\c&H7920CB&}e
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.15,sign_14213_189_Nakano,# sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nakano
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:57.44,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gosh, Mikkun, you're such a meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.48,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding, I'm totally fine with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.41,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, someone's at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.32,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't need to \Nhang up, just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.56,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this will just take a—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.67,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.54,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,They{\i1} all {\i0}asked you out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:15.91,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.31,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,They were all very earnest, and \Nwant me to go out with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:26.00,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's amazing. So, what \Nhappened? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.31,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:32.02,Watamote-flashback,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need an answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:35.78,Watamote-flashback,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted you to know how we felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.24,Watamote-flashback,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this came as a shock to you. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.74,Watamote-flashback,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.75,Watamote-flashback,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted to make sure you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.95,Watamote-flashback,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a lie or a joke. \NThis is how we really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:52.58,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. If they don't need \Nan answer, what's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.91,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,No, they all looked very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.88,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've got to \Ntake this seriously, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.29,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Which means accepting their feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:03.77,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,thinking about them, and \Nthen giving them an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.22,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Or, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.73,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Kae-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.19,Watamote-internal/narrator,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,She's finally grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.80,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.43,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:16.97,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you going to choose? What do \Nyou think of each of them, in summary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.24,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.26,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Igarashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.24,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,5x7!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.22,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.24,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,5x7!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.10,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Mutsumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.99,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He's got that soothing presence \Nthat makes him the perfect top!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.50,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.24,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a klutz, and a definite bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:32.67,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,But depending on his development, \NI think he could switch to a top!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.67,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,And Nishina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.47,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Yokoshima-sensei! A god!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:38.27,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but, Akane-chan is definitely a bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.52,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the fujoshi talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.13,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you seem like you haven't \Nmade any progress at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:47.01,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm s-sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:51.69,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, honestly, I've never looked \Nat them in any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:56.19,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely feel for them. \NThat goes beyond cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:12:01.40,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? What can I do \Nto get to know them all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:06.57,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, if it were an otome game, you \Ncould just follow their character routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.43,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.15,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:15.13,sign_17483_240_Bam,#sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:13.38,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And so, for each day of the \Nholiday next week, I'd like to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.13,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,go on a date with each one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.47,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:17.63,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.61,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And then, at the end of the holidays,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:23.59,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to give my answers to the offers \Nyou each graciously made me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.28,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.27,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.14,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.74,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:34.69,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,The offers we made the other day? She \Nmeans when we asked her out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.99,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,And if she gives us an answer\N after the dates, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.48,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,The dates will decide who wins the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.16,sign_18280_254_Day_1,# box,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Day 1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.16,sign_18280_255_Igarashi_Yusuke,# name,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Igarashi Yusuke
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.16,sign_18280_256_Wanna_go_to_the_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Wanna go to the aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.16,sign_18280_257_Go,# choice left,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.16,sign_18280_258_Don_t_go,# choice right,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Don't go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.62,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:54.19,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty! Look, a shark! Isn't it big?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.73,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that fish looks so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.74,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean the Asian sheepshead wrasse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:02.81,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,They're females when they're young, \Nbut mature into males as they age.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:05.34,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. I'm surprised you know all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.43,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:10.12,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I just Googled it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.95,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.27,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.66,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really answer anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.96,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, how about that—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:21.36,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.09,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:27.78,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Igarashi-kun is very \Nengaging in conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:31.20,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He's very considerate and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.11,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He's really easy to get along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:33.91,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.29,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride the Ferris wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.79,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all the lights! It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.05,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you really are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.90,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And, at times, he says things\N that are really embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.56,sign_18280_254_Day_1,# box,0000,0000,0000,,Day 2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.56,sign_19908_282_Nanashima_Nozomu,# name,0000,0000,0000,,Nanashima Nozomu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.56,sign_19908_283_Let_s_go_to_Usam,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Usami Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.56,sign_19908_284_Go,# choice left,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.56,sign_19908_285_Don_t_go,# choice right,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.50,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is awkward. I gotta \Nsay something! Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.07,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Nanashima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:07.32,Default,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much. Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.56,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:13.10,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta have all the fun you can\Nwhen you come to a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.08,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.66,sign_20478_293_So_cute_,# right,0000,0000,0000,,So Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.66,sign_20478_294_Hee_hee,# mid,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.66,sign_20478_295_giggle,# left,0000,0000,0000,,Giggle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.75,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.55,Default,nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,First, we gotta hit the Usami Coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.54,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Nanashima-kun was a little \Nconstrained at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.42,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,but he loosened up, and was his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.61,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He really knows how to have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.39,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And I had so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:45.04,sign_21044_302_Wah_,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.82,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.99,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Where're \Nyour mommy and daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.56,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some popcorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.15,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,She won't stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.74,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Nanashima-kun, what kind of face is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.94,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You're making my tummy hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.42,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.19,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Ecchan! I looked everywhere for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.51,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.96,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this. And thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.77,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.77,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for some reason, I'm feeling a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:19.84,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Nanashima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.55,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:23.53,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you made her \Nlaugh when she was crying so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.87,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Well, you know I have a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.07,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Kirari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:32.41,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. And she's adored my arsenal \Nof funny faces since she was tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:36.00,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this is what you call gap moe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.79,sign_22459_325_Day_3,# box,0000,0000,0000,,Day 3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.79,sign_22459_326_Shinomiya_Hayato,# name,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya Hayato
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.79,sign_22459_327_Do_you_know_abou,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about the alpaca park?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.79,sign_22459_328_Yeah__I_wanna_go,# choice left,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.79,sign_22459_329_What_s_that__Not,# choice right,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:43.92,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,They're so fluffy. What a view!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.04,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I've got food for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.55,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.45,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I spilled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.34,sign_22767_334_munch__munch,#sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Munch \NMunch
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.92,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair! Shinomiya-kun, \Nit's eating your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.22,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.11,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-kun is the kind of \Nguy you can't leave alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:00.95,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Did I lose any hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.44,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine, you're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.40,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.73,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.94,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a little brother,\NI think it'd feel just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:15.02,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You two over there! Run! \NIt's a wild alpaca!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:18.91,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.17,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-kun! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:28.62,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,It felt so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.17,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:35.40,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. This one \Ncharges any couple he sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.43,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.08,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like, a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.67,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, you can \Nrely on him just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.07,sign_24106_352_Day_4,# box,0000,0000,0000,,Day 4
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.07,sign_24106_353_Nishina_Shima,# name,0000,0000,0000,,Nishina Shima
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.07,sign_24106_354_Shall_we_go_some,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go somewhere good to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.07,sign_24106_355_Go,# choice left,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.07,sign_24106_356_Don_t_go,# choice right,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.57,sign_24227_357_Welcome,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.57,sign_24227_358_Okinawa,,0000,0000,0000,,Okinawa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:57.66,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,This is our restaurant. I've reserved \Nthe whole place, so feel free to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.06,sign_24278_360_Borrowed_her_dre,# box,0000,0000,0000,,Borrowed her dress \Nfrom Shima-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.83,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:03.31,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shima-chan is a celebrity. Every \Nsingle thing she does is elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:06.29,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it feels like we \Nlive in two separate worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.30,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,When I see such beautiful scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:13.22,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me want to put out an \NAkane x Lord honeymoon book!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.72,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see that! So bad! So bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.61,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,They'd start at the venue stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:22.88,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,and then, they wouldn't be able \Nto leave their room for a whole day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.60,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.69,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan would try to leave, \Nand the lord wouldn't let him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.25,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,The lord trying to use \Nhis last chance with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.97,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And Akane-chan would be all about \Nfulfilling his lord's wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:37.53,sign_25245_373_squeal_squeal,# sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Squeal Squeal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:37.53,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,And Akane wouldn't be aware of the fact \Nthat this would be their last time alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.28,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh! A tragedy! That really gets to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:45.19,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,We're soulmates, after all. \NShe's so fun to be around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.21,sign_25559_377_Day_5,# box,0000,0000,0000,,Day 5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.21,sign_25559_378_Mutsumi_Asuma,# name,0000,0000,0000,,Mutsumi Asuma
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.21,sign_25559_379_Shall_we_take_an,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we take an old map and go exploring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.21,sign_25559_380_Go,# choice left,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.21,sign_25559_381_Don_t_go,# choice right,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:52.18,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the old Edo Five Routes start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.88,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? So it doesn't start\Nat the Imperial Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.23,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Is this turn right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.55,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed at all from the Edo era!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:06.06,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. I can't believe there's such \Na forested area within the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.44,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since we're here, shall we pay a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:21.53,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, as always, talks in \Na gentle voice, very softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.41,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He's so kind and soothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.04,Watamote-flashback,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.96,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Was he really serious about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.09,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, what did you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.58,Default,Serinuma,0000,0000,0000,,I wished for the lord and Akane-chan \Nto live happily ever after!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:44.72,sign_26795_394_babble_babble,# sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Babble Babble
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.45,Default,Serinuma,0000,0000,0000,,Also, for Shion to come back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.81,Default,Serinuma,0000,0000,0000,,and for Captain Levi to show his soft side,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:44.72,Default,Serinuma,0000,0000,0000,,and for Miyuki-senpai to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.35,Default,Serinuma,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:51.07,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wished that you and I \Ncould be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:59.30,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I probably always liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:04.12,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But, I didn't know there could \Nbe a special kind of like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:08.56,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, you're the one \Nwho taught me this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.05,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.51,sign_27781_404_A_chan,# phone top,0000,0000,0000,,A-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.51,sign_27781_405_Today,# phone mid,0000,0000,0000,,Today
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.51,sign_27781_406_So__Have_you_mad,# message,0000,0000,0000,,So? Have you made up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.69,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.56,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm even more confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:30.73,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,They're all good people, \Nand have their own charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:34.06,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,They're all kind, and \NI think I like them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.47,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's something just not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.00,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What's missing is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.99,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,that special feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.92,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, god! Who can figure this out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:54.38,Watamote-overlap-top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,We reached out to the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.34,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.05,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,that special feeling is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.17,Watamote-overlap-top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,And gave one devoted prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.78,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,The one I have special feelings for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.92,Watamote-overlap-top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Slash through the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.08,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who she chooses...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.47,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,There are no regrets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.35,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:27.70,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I've found the person that's special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.12,Watamote-internal/narrator,All,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:31.54,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.04,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shion from {\i1}Mirage Saga{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.43,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to air another \Nseason of {\i1}Mirage Saga{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:40.47,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.49,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,There was a silhouette \Nthat had to be Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.93,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could it be?! It has\Nto be him! He's coming back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.51,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,The staff knows what we all love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.19,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all night searching online, and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:51.28,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking through the animators' tweets,\Nbut it looks like production is already going
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.72,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,and they've already started the storyboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.24,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the staff is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.14,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the character\Ndesigner, Kakinuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:59.26,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, the second season will\Ncover the foreshadowing with Panasharu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:00.64,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,and the dagger given to Terra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.48,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many key things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.94,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but there're new characters, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:07.34,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Like, shota twins? Maybe\Nthey're enemies? That's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:08.91,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What if a new pairing is born?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:10.35,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's gotta be Terra x Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.29,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for so long! The day \Nthey'll be together is finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:19.04,sign_30532_444_Mu,# left,0000,0000,0000,,Mu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:19.04,sign_30532_445_Ni,# left mid,0000,0000,0000,,Ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:19.04,sign_30532_446_Shi,# mid,0000,0000,0000,,Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:19.04,sign_30532_447_Nana,# right mid,0000,0000,0000,,Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:19.04,sign_30532_448_Iga,# right,0000,0000,0000,,Iga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:14.59,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.13,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Anime Ito has an early merch exhibit \Ntoday and is taking reservations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.04,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta move! I gotta get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:22.21,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's how it is! Sorry! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.13,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.14,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.68,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about your answer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.27,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-senpai, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.56,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, is that information legit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.44,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san looks like she's \Nhaving a lot of fun! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.95,Default,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:45.15,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,The prince should be with the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.96,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the one who decided that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.72,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,A prince should be with a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.11,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.98,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i0}should{\i1} be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:57.00,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best place \Nfor the princess to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:01.17,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,The princess had a life \Nfull of joy thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.46,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And they all lived happily ever after.
